{
  "id": "68b92c7db98daef100e57d4e",
  "title": "加法定理",
  "created": 1756966016,
  "updated": 1756966303,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "68b92c7db98daef100e57d4e",
      "text": "加法定理",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756966016,
      "updated": 1756966016
    },
    {
      "id": "68b92c7f00000000005a44f1",
      "text": "久々に加法定理の証明をやった[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756966016,
      "updated": 1756966023
    },
    {
      "id": "68b92ca600000000005a452c",
      "text": "\tダルい方法を教わったので難しいイメージを持ってしまっていたが、[$ \\cos(\\alpha-\\beta)]を余弦定理で求める方法ならとても簡単",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756966055,
      "updated": 1756966303
    },
    {
      "id": "68b92cd100000000005a452d",
      "text": " \tダルい方法: [$ \\cos(\\alpha+\\beta)]を先に求める方法。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756966098,
      "updated": 1756966278
    },
    {
      "id": "68b92d8600000000005a452e",
      "text": "  \t結局余弦定理に落とし込むが、最初に図形を回転させる無駄な操作がある。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756966278,
      "updated": 1756966279
    },
    {
      "id": "68b92c8600000000005a44f3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756966023,
      "updated": 1756966023
    },
    {
      "id": "68b92c8600000000005a44f4",
      "text": "加法定理の証明",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756966023,
      "updated": 1756966023
    },
    {
      "id": "68b92c8700000000005a44f5",
      "text": "複素指数関数を用いた証明は思い出すためには有用だが、複素指数関数の定義を考えると循環論法の匂いがする",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756966023,
      "updated": 1756966023
    },
    {
      "id": "68b92c8700000000005a44f6",
      "text": "\t[$ \\cos(\\alpha+\\beta)+i\\sin(\\alpha+\\beta)=e^{i(\\alpha+\\beta)}=e^{i\\alpha}e^{i\\beta}]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756966023,
      "updated": 1756966023
    },
    {
      "id": "68b92c8700000000005a44f7",
      "text": " \t[$ =\\left\\{\\cos(\\alpha)+i\\sin(\\alpha)\\right\\}\\left\\{\\cos(\\beta)+i\\sin(\\beta)\\right\\}]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756966023,
      "updated": 1756966023
    },
    {
      "id": "68b92c8700000000005a44f8",
      "text": "  [$ =\\left\\{\\cos(\\alpha)\\cos(\\beta)-\\sin(\\alpha)\\sin(\\beta)\\right\\}+i\\left\\{\\sin(\\alpha)\\cos(\\beta)+\\cos(\\alpha)\\sin(\\beta)\\right\\}]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756966023,
      "updated": 1756966023
    },
    {
      "id": "68b92c8700000000005a44f9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756966023,
      "updated": 1756966023
    },
    {
      "id": "68b92c8700000000005a44fa",
      "text": "以下の証明を見ると、むしろ複素平面上の積が回転を表すことを、加法定理の証明と同じ方法で示す事になるとわかるだろう。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756966023,
      "updated": 1756966023
    },
    {
      "id": "68b92c8700000000005a44fb",
      "text": "\tベクトルを複素数に取り替えて同じ図を描いて証明することになる。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756966023,
      "updated": 1756966023
    },
    {
      "id": "68b92c8700000000005a44fc",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756966023,
      "updated": 1756966023
    },
    {
      "id": "68b92c8700000000005a44fd",
      "text": "もちろん複素指数関数登場以前から使われている式なので複素数を使わずに幾何的に証明できる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756966023,
      "updated": 1756966023
    },
    {
      "id": "68b92c8700000000005a44fe",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/6d3730cf6045224cdab5e6c185ad74a3][https://gyazo.com/61f039cb469f1d59b5c07cd3d1623591]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756966023,
      "updated": 1756966023
    },
    {
      "id": "68b92c8700000000005a44ff",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756966023,
      "updated": 1756966023
    },
    {
      "id": "68b92c8700000000005a4500",
      "text": "\tこれは複素平面上の点ではなく、単位円上の点",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756966023,
      "updated": 1756966023
    },
    {
      "id": "68b92c8700000000005a4501",
      "text": "\t2つめの画像について",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756966023,
      "updated": 1756966023
    },
    {
      "id": "68b92c8700000000005a4502",
      "text": "\t\t[$ \\cos(2\\pi-x)=\\cos x]なので、[$ \\cos(2\\pi-(\\alpha-\\beta))=\\cos(\\alpha-\\beta)]のようにして左の図と同じ考え方に帰着できる。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756966023,
      "updated": 1756966023
    },
    {
      "id": "68b92c8700000000005a4503",
      "text": "\t余弦定理より",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756966023,
      "updated": 1756966023
    },
    {
      "id": "68b92c8700000000005a4504",
      "text": "\t\t[$ \\left|\\overrightarrow{{\\color{red}\\bull}{\\color{blue}\\bull}}\\right|^2=\\left|\\overrightarrow{O{\\color{red}\\bull}}\\right|^2+\\left|\\overrightarrow{{O\\color{blue}\\bull}}\\right|^2-2\\cos(\\alpha-\\beta)]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756966023,
      "updated": 1756966023
    },
    {
      "id": "68b92c8700000000005a4505",
      "text": "\t\t[$ =1+1-2\\cos(\\alpha-\\beta)]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756966023,
      "updated": 1756966023
    },
    {
      "id": "68b92c8700000000005a4506",
      "text": "\t\t[$ \\cos(\\alpha-\\beta)=1-\\frac12\\left|\\overrightarrow{{\\color{red}\\bull}{\\color{blue}\\bull}}\\right|^2]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756966023,
      "updated": 1756966023
    },
    {
      "id": "68b92c8700000000005a4507",
      "text": "\t\t[$ =1-\\frac12\\left\\{(\\cos\\alpha-\\cos\\beta)^2+(\\sin\\alpha-\\sin\\beta)^2\\right\\}]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756966023,
      "updated": 1756966023
    },
    {
      "id": "68b92c8700000000005a4508",
      "text": "\t\t[$ =1-\\frac12\\{(1-2\\cos\\alpha\\cos\\beta)+(1-2\\sin\\alpha\\sin\\beta)\\}]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756966023,
      "updated": 1756966023
    },
    {
      "id": "68b92c8700000000005a4509",
      "text": "\t\t[$ =\\cos\\alpha\\cos\\beta+\\sin\\alpha\\sin\\beta]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756966023,
      "updated": 1756966023
    },
    {
      "id": "68b92c8700000000005a450a",
      "text": "\t\t[$ \\therefore\\cos(\\alpha-\\beta)=\\cos\\alpha\\cos\\beta+\\sin\\alpha\\sin\\beta]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756966023,
      "updated": 1756966023
    },
    {
      "id": "68b92c8700000000005a450b",
      "text": "\t[$ \\alpha-\\beta=0]の場合",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756966023,
      "updated": 1756966023
    },
    {
      "id": "68b92c8700000000005a450c",
      "text": "\t\t[$ \\cos(\\alpha-\\beta)=\\cos0=1]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756966023,
      "updated": 1756966023
    },
    {
      "id": "68b92c8700000000005a450d",
      "text": "\t\t[$ \\cos\\alpha\\cos\\beta+\\sin\\alpha\\sin\\beta=\\cos^2\\alpha+\\sin^2\\beta=1\\qquad(\\because\\alpha=\\beta)]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756966023,
      "updated": 1756966023
    },
    {
      "id": "68b92c8700000000005a450e",
      "text": "\t[$ \\alpha-\\beta=\\pi]の場合",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756966023,
      "updated": 1756966023
    },
    {
      "id": "68b92c8700000000005a450f",
      "text": "\t\t[$ \\cos(\\alpha-\\beta)=\\cos\\pi=-1]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756966023,
      "updated": 1756966023
    },
    {
      "id": "68b92c8700000000005a4510",
      "text": "\t\t[$ \\cos\\alpha\\cos\\beta+\\sin\\alpha\\sin\\beta=\\cos(\\pi+\\beta)\\cos\\beta+\\sin(\\pi+\\beta)\\sin\\beta\\qquad(\\because\\alpha=\\pi+\\beta)]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756966023,
      "updated": 1756966023
    },
    {
      "id": "68b92c8700000000005a4511",
      "text": " \t\t[$ =-\\cos\\beta\\cos\\beta-\\sin\\beta\\sin\\beta=-1]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756966023,
      "updated": 1756966023
    },
    {
      "id": "68b92c8700000000005a4512",
      "text": "\tよって左辺と右辺の成立を任意の[$ \\alpha-\\beta\\in\\R]について確認できたことになる。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756966023,
      "updated": 1756966023
    },
    {
      "id": "68b92c8700000000005a4513",
      "text": "\t\t[$ 0\\le\\alpha-\\beta<2\\pi]の場合について示せれば[$ 2\\pi]倍については三角関数は同じ値になるのですべて確認したことになる。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756966023,
      "updated": 1756966023
    },
    {
      "id": "68b92c8700000000005a4514",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756966023,
      "updated": 1756966023
    },
    {
      "id": "68b92c8700000000005a4515",
      "text": " 残りの加法定理は芋づる式に手に入る",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756966023,
      "updated": 1756966023
    },
    {
      "id": "68b92c8700000000005a4516",
      "text": " [$ \\cos(\\alpha+\\beta)]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756966023,
      "updated": 1756966023
    },
    {
      "id": "68b92c8700000000005a4517",
      "text": " \t[$ =\\cos(\\alpha-(-\\beta))]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756966023,
      "updated": 1756966023
    },
    {
      "id": "68b92c8700000000005a4518",
      "text": " \t[$ =\\cos\\alpha\\cos(-\\beta)+\\sin\\alpha\\sin(-\\beta)]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756966023,
      "updated": 1756966023
    },
    {
      "id": "68b92c8700000000005a4519",
      "text": " \t[$ =\\cos\\alpha\\cos\\beta-\\sin\\alpha\\sin\\beta]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756966023,
      "updated": 1756966023
    },
    {
      "id": "68b92c8700000000005a451a",
      "text": " [$ \\sin(\\alpha-\\beta)]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756966023,
      "updated": 1756966023
    },
    {
      "id": "68b92c8700000000005a451b",
      "text": " \t[$ =\\cos\\left((\\alpha-\\beta)-\\pi/2\\right)]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756966023,
      "updated": 1756966023
    },
    {
      "id": "68b92c8700000000005a451c",
      "text": " \t[$ =\\cos\\left(\\alpha-\\left(\\beta+\\pi/2\\right)\\right)]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756966023,
      "updated": 1756966023
    },
    {
      "id": "68b92c8700000000005a451d",
      "text": " \t[$ =\\cos\\alpha\\cos\\left(\\beta+\\pi/2\\right)+\\sin\\alpha\\sin\\left(\\beta+\\pi/2\\right)]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756966023,
      "updated": 1756966023
    },
    {
      "id": "68b92c8700000000005a451e",
      "text": " \t[$ =\\cos\\alpha\\{-\\sin\\beta\\}+\\sin\\alpha\\cos\\beta]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756966023,
      "updated": 1756966023
    },
    {
      "id": "68b92c8700000000005a451f",
      "text": " \t[$ =\\sin\\alpha\\cos\\beta-\\cos\\alpha\\sin\\beta]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756966023,
      "updated": 1756966023
    },
    {
      "id": "68b92c8700000000005a4520",
      "text": "\t[$ \\sin(\\alpha+\\beta)]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756966023,
      "updated": 1756966023
    },
    {
      "id": "68b92c8700000000005a4521",
      "text": "\t\t[$ =\\sin\\left(\\alpha-(-\\beta)\\right)]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756966023,
      "updated": 1756966023
    },
    {
      "id": "68b92c8700000000005a4522",
      "text": "\t\t[$ =\\sin\\alpha\\cos(-\\beta)-\\cos\\alpha\\sin(-\\beta)]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756966023,
      "updated": 1756966023
    },
    {
      "id": "68b92c8700000000005a4523",
      "text": "\t\t[$ =\\sin\\alpha\\cos\\beta+\\cos\\alpha\\sin\\beta]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756966023,
      "updated": 1756966023
    },
    {
      "id": "68b92c8700000000005a4524",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756966023,
      "updated": 1756966023
    },
    {
      "id": "68b92c8700000000005a4525",
      "text": "この証明には対称性に関する定理を用いているが、それらも単位円上の対称な点に関する図を描いて示せる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756966023,
      "updated": 1756966023
    },
    {
      "id": "68b92c8700000000005a4526",
      "text": "\t[https://gyazo.com/9b6daa4ab800e31ca3d896dcf65fcece]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756966023,
      "updated": 1756966023
    },
    {
      "id": "68b92c8700000000005a4527",
      "text": "\t軸[$ -\\frac\\pi2,0,\\frac\\pi2,\\pi]に対してαを足したり引いたり座標と、軸を別の始線とみなしてαの角度から求めた[$ \\pm\\cos\\alpha,\\pm\\sin\\alpha]のみで表された座標を結びつけることで一般角に対して対称性公式の成立を示せる。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756966023,
      "updated": 1756966023
    },
    {
      "id": "68b92c8700000000005a4528",
      "text": "\t\t↑角度を制限させないために、直角三角形という言葉を使わないのがミソ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756966023,
      "updated": 1756966023
    },
    {
      "id": "68b92c8700000000005a4529",
      "text": "\t\t図では見やすくするために[$ 0<\\alpha<\\frac\\pi4]にしているが、一般角αに対して同じ図を描いても同じ結果を得る。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756966023,
      "updated": 1756966023
    },
    {
      "id": "68b92c8700000000005a452a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756966023,
      "updated": 1756966023
    },
    {
